! IEEE 13 × DER 25%
! Total PV = 25% of 3,466 kW ≈ 867 kW, split equally across 3 buses (≈ 289 kW each)
! Bus placement:
!   671 (primary load 1,155 kW, 4.16 kV Delta): PV_671
!   675 (primary load 843 kW, 4.16 kV Wye):     PV_675
!   634 (secondary of XFM-1, 480 V Wye):        PV_634

